### Get all employees
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/employees
Accept: application/json

### Get single employee
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/employees/1
Accept: application/json

### Create new employee
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/employees
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "first_name": "John",
    "last_name": "Doe",
    "email": "john.doe@example.com",
    "password": "secret123",
    "color": "#FF5733",
    "department_id": 1,
    "is_admin": false
}

### Update employee
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/employees/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "first_name": "John",
    "last_name": "Smith",
    "email": "john.smith@example.com",
    "color": "#33FF57",
    "department_id": 1,
    "is_admin": false
}

### Delete employee
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/employees/1
Accept: application/json

### Get employees by department
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/employees/department/1
Accept: application/json

### Get employee shifts
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/employees/shifts/1
Accept: application/json
